00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:22.270
The matrix [INAUDIBLE] and
this is just alpha t over 2.

00:14:22.270 --> 00:14:24.710
And the energy of
the second state

00:14:24.710 --> 00:14:27.410
is going to be minus
alpha t over 2.

00:14:30.430 --> 00:14:35.530
We can plot those
energies, and here

00:14:35.530 --> 00:14:45.490
