00:15:57.720 --> 00:16:04.380
I claim, actually, that the true
solutions of the Schrodinger

00:16:04.380 --> 00:16:09.360
equation are in
this case dressed up

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:14.730
versions of the instantaneous
energy eigenstates.

00:16:14.730 --> 00:16:17.160
So what I claim is
the kind of-- you

00:16:17.160 --> 00:16:20.230
do the adiabatic state
corresponding to this,

00:16:20.230 --> 00:16:22.860
the adiabatic state
corresponding to that,

00:16:22.860 --> 00:16:25.870
and those are exact solutions.

00:16:25.870 --> 00:16:30.960
So there is no coupling
between the states, 1 and 2.

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:32.780
So this is plausible.

00:16:32.780 --> 00:16:36.990
So let's write those solutions.

