00:18:37.890 --> 00:18:39.500
OK.

00:18:39.500 --> 00:18:41.690
Let's appreciate
the lesson again.

00:18:41.690 --> 00:18:48.870
We got a very simple system,
two levels, crossing--

00:18:48.870 --> 00:18:50.180
